Alternatively you may want to send the data to another program that can parse the raw buffer\&.
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
# nvme id\-ns /dev/nvme0n1 \-\-raw\-binary | nvme_parse_id_ns
.fi
